  dialogue:
  - If your going to go on a adventure it might be wise to practice a bit before
    heading out, PRESS [E] TO PROGRESS DIALOGUE.
  - It's important to know how to use your wool!
  - Use [Tab] to select your wool.
  - Then Hold [Left Click] to aim with the mouse.
  - Release [Left Click] to fire!
  - Your normal wool can be used to create platforms.
